comedians comfortable.

1502
00:48:15,108 --> 00:48:16,108
I feel comfortable.

1503
00:48:16,108 --> 00:48:17,608
(An honorary comedian)

1504
00:48:18,118 --> 00:48:19,948
Eun I's company is that way.

1505
00:48:19,948 --> 00:48:21,718
- That way.
- Yes, up there.

1506
00:48:21,718 --> 00:48:23,348
You must often eat around here.

1507
00:48:23,348 --> 00:48:24,818
Yes. But I don't come this far.

1508
00:48:25,358 --> 00:48:26,888
We normally eat at the old section of Sangam-dong.

1509
00:48:26,888 --> 00:48:28,628
But you know the leaf wraps and rice place.

1510
00:48:28,628 --> 00:48:30,558
Yes. They also give you tteokbokki.

1511
